24:05.850 --> 24:08.873
And for the most part, it's not with regard to Christ.

24:10.274 --> 24:12.016
It's not with regard to righteousness.

24:12.136 --> 24:13.197
It's the very opposite.

24:13.498 --> 24:17.341
And it's just constantly, constantly, constantly chipping away.

24:18.142 --> 24:20.505
Now, let me say one other thing.

24:21.105 --> 24:21.506
All right.

24:22.707 --> 24:25.970
Man, I am in a few days, I'm going to be 64.

24:26.882 --> 24:30.767
And I have been in the ministry for over 40 years.

24:33.150 --> 24:35.152
Um, I read the Bible quite a bit.

24:35.192 --> 24:43.763
I know that I can't listen over and over to these things.

24:44.244 --> 24:50.051
I know that when I hear people speak contrary to Christ, I need to get out of there.

24:50.071 --> 24:53.815
I know that if there's entertainment, I need to get out of there.

24:53.936 --> 24:55.858
If it's contrary to Christ, why?

24:57.090 --> 25:03.800
because little by little, it will start having an impact even on someone like me.

25:04.782 --> 25:05.883
Now how much more?

25:07.346 --> 25:15.859
If you're just a kid, maybe a brand new Christian, you can't even find the book of Philippians.

25:15.939 --> 25:16.319
All right.

25:20.806 --> 25:22.308
Do you see how you should be careful?

25:23.690 --> 25:24.091
Look at me.

25:24.151 --> 25:26.034
I'm looking at you the best I can.

25:28.834 --> 25:39.411
You need to increase in the fear of sin and you need to increase in the fear of self and you need to increase in your fear or reverence for the Lord.

25:40.372 --> 25:40.893
Let's pray.

25:44.539 --> 25:45.761
Father, I pray.

25:45.781 --> 25:52.471
Oh God, please work in their heart.

25:53.473 --> 25:56.658
These children, these teenagers, parents,

26:01.218 --> 26:02.139
It's a battlefield.

26:02.199 --> 26:03.761
It's a war zone, Lord.

26:05.443 --> 26:07.246
And it's so easy to be swept away.

26:09.248 --> 26:26.930
Please, dear God, work in the heart of your people, save children and teenagers from the condemnation of sin and the power of it and the influence of it.

26:27.938 --> 26:34.469
Lord, if there are young people that are in relationships that are dangerous, I pray that you would break them.

26:36.011 --> 26:45.206
Break those relationships and create for them new relationships that promote love for Christ and righteousness.

26:46.147 --> 26:49.172
Dear God, I ask all this in Jesus' name.

26:49.773 --> 26:50.194
Amen.

